#: ../../source/reference/learn/generated/maxframe.learn.preprocessing.normalize.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.learn.preprocessing.normalize"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.learn.preprocessing._data.normalize.normalize:1 of
msgid "Scale input vectors individually to unit norm (vector length)."
msgstr "将输入向量各自缩放到单位范数（向量长度）。"

#: ../../source/reference/learn/generated/maxframe.learn.preprocessing.normalize.rst
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.learn.preprocessing._data.normalize.normalize:3 of
msgid ""
"The data to normalize, element by element. scipy.sparse matrices should "
"be in CSR format to avoid an un-necessary copy."
msgstr "要逐元素归一化的数据。scipy.sparse 矩阵应为 CSR 格式以避免不必要的复制。"

#: maxframe.learn.preprocessing._data.normalize.normalize:7 of
msgid ""
"The norm to use to normalize each non zero sample (or each non-zero "
"feature if axis is 0)."
msgstr "用于归一化每个非零样本（如果 axis 为 0，则为每个非零特征）的范数。"

#: maxframe.learn.preprocessing._data.normalize.normalize:10 of
msgid ""
"axis used to normalize the data along. If 1, independently normalize each"
" sample, otherwise (if 0) normalize each feature."
msgstr ""
"用于沿着进行数据归一化的轴。如果为 1，则独立地归一化每个样本；否则（如果"
"为 0）归一化每个特征。"

#: maxframe.learn.preprocessing._data.normalize.normalize:13 of
msgid ""
"set to False to perform inplace row normalization and avoid a copy (if "
"the input is already a tensor and if axis is 1)."
msgstr ""
"设为 False 以执行原地行归一化并避免复制（如果输入已经是张量并且 axis 为 1"
"）。"

#: maxframe.learn.preprocessing._data.normalize.normalize:16 of
msgid "whether to return the computed norms"
msgstr "是否返回计算出的范数"

#: ../../source/reference/learn/generated/maxframe.learn.preprocessing.normalize.rst
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.learn.preprocessing._data.normalize.normalize:19 of
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"* **X** (*{array-like, sparse matrix}, shape [n_samples, n_features]*) --"
" Normalized input X. * **norms** (*Tensor, shape [n_samples] if axis=1 "
"else [n_features]*) -- A tensor of norms along given axis for X.   When X"
" is sparse, a NotImplementedError will be raised   for norm 'l1' or 'l2'."
msgstr ""
"* **X** (*{array-like, sparse matrix}, shape [n_samples, n_features]*) --"
" 归一化后的输入 X。* **norms** (*Tensor, shape [n_samples] if axis=1 else"
" [n_features]*) -- 沿着给定轴的 X 的范数张量。当 X 是稀疏矩阵时，对于 'l1"
"' 或 'l2' 范数会抛出 NotImplementedError。"

#: maxframe.learn.preprocessing._data.normalize.normalize:19 of
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"**X** (*{array-like, sparse matrix}, shape [n_samples, n_features]*) -- "
"Normalized input X."
msgstr ""
"**X** (*{array-like, sparse matrix}, shape [n_samples, n_features]*) -- "
"归一化后的输入 X。"

#: maxframe.learn.preprocessing._data.normalize.normalize:20 of
msgid ""
"**norms** (*Tensor, shape [n_samples] if axis=1 else [n_features]*) -- A "
"tensor of norms along given axis for X. When X is sparse, a "
"NotImplementedError will be raised for norm 'l1' or 'l2'."
msgstr ""
"**norms** (*Tensor, shape [n_samples] if axis=1 else [n_features]*) -- "
"沿着给定轴的 X 的范数张量。当 X 是稀疏矩阵时，对于 'l1' 或 'l2' 范数会"
"抛出 NotImplementedError。"

#: maxframe.learn.preprocessing._data.normalize.normalize:26 of
msgid ":py:obj:`Normalizer`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.learn.preprocessing._data.normalize.normalize:27 of
msgid ""
"Performs normalization using the ``Transformer`` API (e.g. as part of a "
"preprocessing :class:`maxframe.learn.pipeline.Pipeline`)."
msgstr ""
"使用 ``Transformer`` API 执行归一化（例如作为预处理 :class:`maxframe."
"learn.pipeline.Pipeline` 的一部分）。"

